# Dependencies
#-------------

The following libraries are required to compile/run ZArt:

 - libqt4-dev
 - libcv2.1
 - libcvaux2.1
 - libcvaux-dev
 - libcv-dev
 - libhighgui2.1
 - libhighgui-dev
 - libfftw3-3
 - libfftw3-dev

